// Web-grounded knowledge base (built 2026-06-22 via a multi-agent workflow that
// searched authoritative sources — WHO / NHS / APA / NIMH / NCBI / Mayo / Cleveland
// Clinic / Mind / YoungMinds / Self-Compassion / Sleep Foundation, etc. — and
